yo0o..wuzza pplz...well its been goin pretty good 4 me i guess.well not really,im lieing but w/e i jus tell my self cuz its tru wut everyone says,im a lil 2 dramatic sometimes...i dun wanna be known 4 that but w/e i really dun care wut ppl think about me...i remember last year i would always denpend on what ppl would say...now,i use what they say 2 wipe my ass.i got tired after a while of listening 2 everyones shit and having 2 live up 2 their expectations..i mean whos life it is mine or theirs?w/e...enuff if that shit...yesterday we went bowling...well i dun knowe if u would call it bowling..nun of us bowled we jus went 2 the bowling alley and chilled played in the arcades 4 a while until i got thrown out and everyone came wit me cuz they didnt wanna leave me by myself so we jus went 2 go chill and play pool...i came home and couldnt sleep cuz that day i was playin football and i hit jonathon 2 hard and i dun kno wen i got up my hip hurt and the next mouring it was a bitch 2 get outta bed...i called denise we talked 4 a while and she was telling me she was goin shopping (lucky bitch..lol j/k) she was goin 2 like 3 different stores..i met up wit her in international...she was wit her mom and i was wit my parents...shes always saying she wanted 2 meet them so i was like where u at so u can meet them...well after she met them she asked me if i wanted 2 stay wit her cuz we were both goin 2 dolfin and it would be pretty cool 2 chill 4 a while i guess.her mom's down as fuk! denise,dun let ne one else tell u different...shes really cool...w/e we got 2 dolfin like at 9 we were gonna watch a movie but it was already 2 late... so we chilled wit these ppl and denise had a really bad headache so we didnt really walk much...sumtin happ[en wit jonathon and eric..."GRLS"..its always grls...it never fails...w/e me juan nadya denise and denise's frend albert (hes down as fuk 2) we all went up stairs 2 chill and eat shit...and guess who we ran into...kevin and miguel wit some 2 ugly ass hoes...sumtin happen wit juan and miguel and miguel wanted 2 fight..i was goin crazy... he threw down his chair and started walkin toward juan....i was like yes..i hope this shit goes down...well not really cuz nadya and denise were there and we didnt wanna get them involved...and its funny cuz all juan wanted 2 do was talk 2 him and miguel was trying 2 act all hard n shit...i was like who the fuk does the punk nigga think he is??nadya was holding me bak and denise was holding bak juan.i woulda loved 4 juan 2 throw a punch... i was talking 2 that nigga albert he was sayin that if he threw a punch he was gonna get in it and fuk that nigga up...he wasnt that big but he looks like a kinda kid that knows hoe 2 fight.w/e and then we went in i read some baseball book... and then we all went down stairs and chilled..then we went outside...i saw my mom...she passed right by me..i sware i chased her in her car 4 mayb about 5 mins...i was TIRED as fuk...i got into the car sweating bullets...and now im tired as fuk and my stomach hurts.so im out ill update this shit 2mrw if i have time...latez

well..i havent updated this shit mayb in like 3 days...not much has happend.jus that the person i care about most now its outta my life.its ok i mean im not really sure what the situation is,but i have an idea.i mean i dun kno 4 sure...but something tells me im right.she said soemthing that meant alot...and like an asshole i got my hopes up.esoecially wit sometin i really never have luck wit.it happen 2 me once and it took me a WHILE 2 get over the person..i have a feeling im gonna have 2 be doin that again.i mean i kno its not gonna take half as much as it took me b4,but i dun wanna even wanna go through this shit 4 another day.if sumone ever granted u a wish,most ppl would ask 4 money,a huge house,or everything they've ever wannted...u wanna kno what i would wish for.a gun,wit jus one bullet,so i can get the fuk outta this world.i mean i kno alot of kids have it alot worse then i do.im only missing one thing that makes it feel like everything.4 some reason i feel like im missing everything.my frends,my family,EVERYTHING.i jus dont kno how she can do this 2 me.i can get through this.i jus wanna kno how long it'll take me.but even if i think about it even if i did get what i wanted it really wouldnt make a differemce.im not gonna say y cuz it would make it obvious of who im talkin bout and i dun  wanna ne one 2 kno.i jus wanna look bak on this in a few years wen i make it big without ne of the ppl in my life now and realize how bad i had it and how good i have it then.w/e this shit aint gonna break me down.ill save my tears 4 something more important.i need 2 aggravate my sefl for some stupid ass shit like this all i gotta do is 4 get.it might jus take me a while cuz me and the person r really good frends...and even after all of this i hope thats what we stay."Really good frends"
